      "widgets_values": [
        "# Manual Audio Surgery\n\n1. Load original audio\n2. Transcribe and build SRT\n3. Edit only the target cues in the SRT editor\n4. Regenerate the replacement cues with IndexTTS\n5. Optionally post-edit the regenerated cue with Step Audio EditX\n6. Use AudioConcat / Merge Audio to stitch edited slices back with untouched audio parts"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653",
      "title": "Workflow Note"
